{"tid":49603,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"打fifa發現中國地圖無台灣 強國人大發雷霆！！","createTime":"2016-12-21T23:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T02:27:21.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a76e291dbfde7114566a9dd14fd695bb888ff6c","tid":49603,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:41:49.000Z","msg":"有網友在《批踢踢實業坊》表示「剛剛看左岸的主播播FIFA，中華人民共和國台灣竟然不包括在內，結果主播整個崩潰，觀眾也暴動惹」，並po上2張電玩遊戲擷圖，這就是怎麼一回事呢？<br />\n <br />\n原來是知名遊戲大廠「藝電」(EA)所推出的《國際足盟大賽》(FIFA)中，中國的領土(標示為黃色)範圍沒有包含台灣，中國的一名實況主播便相當崩潰，觀眾們也很生氣，有人乾脆親自「手動」替台灣後製、塗上黃色，讓許多網友傻眼。其他鄉民們看了則回應：「繼SEGA之後 EA也要道歉了嗎」、「EA要發布更新檔了」、「中國人最喜歡幹這種事」、「我到底看了三小」、「玩個遊戲整天在那邊玻璃心」、「講實在 沒台灣的中國地圖很漂亮」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2mpp94E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2mpp94E.jpg&h=0af7a943&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/074051_2e554315f0f2e293ebe30165f15240a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F074051_2e554315f0f2e293ebe30165f15240a7.jpg&h=7ec63e23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"221d927a87ab48860a889d80821661714de63747","tid":49603,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:59:15.000Z","msg":"太好笑喇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b019caa52055a38cd506721d3dfed26070fa8517","tid":49603,"uid":11963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:06:05.000Z","msg":"玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43247b679c12c85ddd19b9c2cfc5ae936ca8f0d4","tid":49603,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br